      "span_text": "[1] The prevalence of football injuries has increased in recent years, in addition to the greater number of injuries in comparison to other sports.  Investigating football injuries according to their type, the reasons for the higher incidence rates, the injury mechanisms, and the most affected anatomic sites will facilitate the development of management strategies in health care, especially in preventive medicine."
